package main

help_text :: `
Mimir - AI Chat CLI

Usage:
  mimir --ask (-a)            Ask the LLM a one-off question.
  mimir --chat (-c)           Chat with the LLM.
  mimir --clear-chat (-clrc)  Clear the chat session data, makes the LLM 'Forget'. 
  mimir --help (-h)           Show this help
  mimir --version (-v)        Show version
`
